# Whitelist approach — ignore everything in the repo root by default,
# then opt-in to what we want tracked. Keeps the deck (.pptx),
# screenshot library (figs/, install/), build artifacts, and any other
# loose docs out of the repo unless they're explicitly un-ignored.

/*
!.gitignore
!README.md
!TROUBLESHOOTING_LOG.md
!CLAUDE.md
!manifest.yaml
!bootstrap-fresh-pve.sh
!automation/
!addons/
